210
00:22:28,015 --> 00:22:28,195
Yeah.

211
00:22:28,815 --> 00:22:55,602
And again, I think the intent here as written is, you know, legal service will be solely in service of the council may include research analysis and drafting assistance and that the legal services provided the council will not include representation of the council or any counselor in any court matter or related litigation or the issuance of formal legal opinions on behalf of the state is really intended to avoid that conflict, but still allow the council to have advice and research and analysis

212
00:22:56,740 --> 00:23:01,882
independent in some cases of the, I can see a potential conflict.

213
00:23:01,922 --> 00:23:10,706
